{"tid":1334474,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[721]前線同和理非，你做足準備未？","createTime":"2019-07-20T06:21:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T11:47:33.000Z","uid":89974,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"fd8d644aa3653987b8c0d87b0122c3042139a284","tid":1334474,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:21:11.000Z","msg":"1.聽日可能有黑社會搞事，可能會有狗亂咬人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救人啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n2.和理非同勇武都要full gear，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">救人啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3.鬥爭可避則避，但如避無可避一定要郁手，係cam面前讀咗呢段先盡量保護自己：<br />\n如打人：<br />\n你襲擊39，現在行使公民拘捕權！(最好比佢實質打中先用，否則未必入到)<br />\n<br />\n如有傷害：<br />\n你傷人19，現在行使公民拘補權！<br />\n<br />\n如有黑社會自爆：<br />\n你聲稱三合會成員，現在行使公民拘補權！<br />\n<br />\n如有冒警人士兼有帶攻擊性武器(記住一定要有埋武器先可以，否則唔夠level用)：<br />\n你非法管有攻擊性武器，現在行使公民拘補權！<br />\n<br />\n4.制服完開遮遮住鏡頭做咩就自己醒水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5.見到有人比人捉走唔撚好再食花生，一定要帶齊gear<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">救人救人救人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n6. TO 和理非：有數得計，我地每輸一次就輸60個兄弟，你自己計下輸幾多次之後你就要上前線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.警察落charge還警察落charge，法庭判你罪還法庭判你罪，我無野講我要見律師我要飲水食飯我要去廁所我要去醫院，其他野唔撚好講啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ef0f3258899a8aa4608d3dda822d2363d0a618d","tid":1334474,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:21:15.000Z","msg":"OYSG"},{"pid":"c6b3a0ad06b05007aadffadcc04bea8bce95a32f","tid":1334474,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:25:06.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"cbc16e341564876b8013c98ef322048243270e17","tid":1334474,"uid":89974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"